[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m20[0m[39m:import java.io.InputStream;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m21[0m[39m:import java.nio.charset.StandardCharsets;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m22[0m[39m:import java.security.GeneralSecurityException;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m23[0m[39m:import java.security.KeyStore;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m24[0m[39m:import java.util.HashMap;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m25[0m[39m:import java.util.HashSet;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m26[0m[39m:import java.util.List;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m27[0m[39m:import java.util.Map;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m28[0m[39m:import java.util.Set;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m29[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m30[0m[39m:import org.apache.logging.log4j.Logger;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m31[0m[39m:import org.apache.logging.log4j.LogManager;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m32[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSArray;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSBase;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSDictionary;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSDocument;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSName;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSNull;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSNumber;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m39[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSObject;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m40[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSObjectKey;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSStream;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.ICOSParser;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m43[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.IOUtils;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessRead;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m45[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessReadView;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m46[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.io.RandomAccessStreamCache.StreamCacheCreateFunction;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m47[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.encryption.AccessPermission;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m48[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.encryption.DecryptionMaterial;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m49[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.encryption.InvalidPasswordException;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.encryption.PDEncryption;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m51[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.encryption.ProtectionPolicy;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m52[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.encryption.PublicKeyDecryptionMaterial;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m53[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.encryption.SecurityHandler;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m54[0m[39m:import org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.encryption.StandardDecryptionMaterial;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/contentstream/PDFStreamEngine.jav[0m[1;92ma:87[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m97[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m87[0m[39m:    private PDPage currentPage;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m88[0m[39m:    private boolean isProcessingPage;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:    private Matrix initialMatrix;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m used to monitor potentially recursive operations.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:    private int level = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m default font, used if there isn't any font available[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:    private PDFont defaultFont;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m96[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m97[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m false in certain cases, e.g. type3 charprocs with d1 or uncolored tiling [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatterns[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis of the Timeout Issue[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBased on the comprehensive code analysis, the libFuzzer timeout persists because [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe previous patch only addressed **recursion depth** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvertical limits[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but did not[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddress **iteration counts and byte-read limits** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mhorizontal limits[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. The timeout [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs due to multiple unbounded loops throughout the parsing infrastructure.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Causes Identified[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Unbounded dictionary parsing**: `[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` has no limit on the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnumber of key-value pairs[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Unbounded array parsing**: `[0m[1;35mparseCOSArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` has no limit on the number of [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39melements[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Unbounded stream reading**: `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` can read indefinitely when [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream length is invalid[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Unbounded error recovery**: `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and hex string [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecovery loops read byte-by-byte without limits[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **String parsing loops**: Various string parsing methods have unbounded loops[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch's depth limit of [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m still allows enormous structures [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnested arrays, each with thousands of elements[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Reapply Previous Depth Limiting Patch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwith modifications[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `BaseParser.java`:**[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reintroduce `parsingDepth`, `[0m[1;35mincreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mdecreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Reduce `MAX_PARSING_DEPTH` from [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m25[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmore aggressive limit for fuzzing[0m[1;39m)[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Maintain the try-finally pattern in `[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mparseCOSArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Add Iteration Count Limits for Arrays and Dictionaries[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `BaseParser.java`:**[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add constant: `MAX_COLLECTION_ELEMENTS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Add iteration counter before the while loop, increment[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min each iteration, throw IOException if exceeded[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mparseCOSArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Add iteration counter before the while loop, increment in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meach iteration, throw IOException if exceeded[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This prevents malformed PDFs from creating dictionaries/arrays with millions of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39melements at a single depth level[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: Even shallow structures can timeout if they contain thousands of [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39melements. This limits the width of structures at each level.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Implement Stream Size Limits[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `COSParser.java`:**[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch already added `MAX_STREAM_SIZE = 500L * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m` but didn't utilize[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Add a byte counter that accumulates `contentBytes` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwritten to the output stream[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Before writing to output stream [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m869[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, check if total bytes exceed [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`MAX_STREAM_SIZE`[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- If exceeded, throw IOException with message indicating stream size limit reached[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This prevents reading gigabytes of stream data[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: The `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method is called when stream length [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation fails. Without limits, it can read entire large files byte-by-byte.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Add Byte-Read Limits for Error Recovery Methods[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `BaseParser.java`:**[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add constant: `MAX_ERROR_RECOVERY_BYTES = [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m1MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Add byte counter, increment in while loop, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrow IOException if exceeded[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mparseCOSHexString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` error recovery loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m727[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m731[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Add byte counter, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrow IOException if exceeded[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: Error recovery paths are triggered by malformed PDFs and can read [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmassive amounts of data. Limiting these prevents timeout in error scenarios.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Add Iteration Limits for String Parsing[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `BaseParser.java`:**[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add constant: `MAX_STRING_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m10MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mparseCOSString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Track bytes written to ByteArrayOutputStream, throw [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException if exceeded[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mparseCOSHexString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Track StringBuilder length, throw IOException if [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexceeded[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mreadString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Track buffer length, throw IOException if exceeded[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mparseCOSName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Track buffer length, throw IOException if exceeded[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: While strings are typically short, malformed PDFs can have extremely[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlong strings that cause timeouts.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Add Total Operation Counter [0m[1;39m([0m[39mGlobal Safety Net[0m[1;39m)[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `BaseParser.java`:**[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add instance variable: `totalParsingOperations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add constant: `MAX_TOTAL_OPERATIONS = [0m[1;36m1000000[0m[39m`[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Increment counter in hot paths: beginning of `[0m[1;35mparseDirObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mparseCOSArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check counter and throw IOException if exceeded[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reset counter when starting fresh parse[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: Even with all individual limits, combinations of operations could [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill timeout. A global operation counter provides a final safety net.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m. Preserve Existing Functionality[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Critical preservation points:**[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Do not modify the core parsing logic, only add guards[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All limits should throw IOException with descriptive messages [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot silently fail[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Use try-finally blocks to ensure depth counters are properly decremented[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check for EOF conditions to avoid infinite loops reading [0m[1;36m-1[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Maintain lenient mode behavior [0m[1;39m([0m[39merror recovery attempts before failing[0m[1;39m)[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Do not break existing test compatibility[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m. Implementation Order and Integration[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Apply limits in this order:**[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Reapply depth limiting with reduced MAX_PARSING_DEPTH [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m25[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add collection element limits [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdictionaries and arrays[0m[1;39m)[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Add stream size limit in `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Add error recovery byte limits[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Add string parsing length limits[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Add global operation counter[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Integration considerations:**[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All new limits should log warnings when approached [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., at [0m[1;36m90[0m[39m% of limit[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Limits should be declared as `protected static final` constants at the class [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlevel[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Counter variables should be instance variables reset for each parse[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Use existing LOG infrastructure for warnings and errors[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This is Optimal[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Multi-layered defense**: Addresses all identified timeout sources [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msimultaneously[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Maintains backward compatibility**: Only adds guards, doesn't change core [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Follows existing patterns**: Uses same depth-limiting pattern as [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDFStreamEngine[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Graceful degradation**: Allows parsing of valid PDFs while rejecting [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalicious/malformed ones[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Fuzzing-friendly**: Limits are tuned for fuzzing time constraints while [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallowing reasonable PDF structures[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Preserves Existing Logic[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All limits are additive guards, not modifications to parsing algorithms[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Error paths still attempt recovery before failing[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Valid PDFs will never hit these limits in practice[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Lenient mode behavior is maintained within safe bounds[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses the Evaluation Report[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Depth limiting**: Reapplied with reduced threshold [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m25[0m[39m instead of [0m[1;36m50[0m[1;39m)[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Stream size limiting**: Actually implements the unused MAX_STREAM_SIZE constant[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Iteration limiting**: Addresses the [0m[32m"wide structure"[0m[39m problem [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmany elements per[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlevel[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Error recovery limiting**: Prevents byte-by-byte reading timeouts[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Global safety net**: Operation counter catches any remaining edge cases[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Side effect**: Legitimate very large PDFs might be rejected[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Limits are generous [0m[1;39m([0m[39m10K elements per collection, 500MB [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstreams[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Side effect**: Complex but valid PDFs might hit depth limit of [0m[1;36m25[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: [0m[1;36m25[0m[39m levels of nesting is far beyond typical PDF complexity[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Side effect**: Error messages might be less specific [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlimit exceeded vs. [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mactual parse error[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Log descriptive messages with context [0m[1;39m([0m[39mposition, limit type[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Reference to Similar Codebase Solutions[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe existing `PDFStreamEngine` class [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m92[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m1160[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1177[0m[39m, DrawObject.java lines [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m70[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m85[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m demonstrates the depth limiting pattern:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Instance variable for level tracking[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Increase/decrease methods[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check against limit [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m50[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with error logging[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Used in try-finally blocks[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis fix strategy extends that pattern to the parser and adds complementary [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwidth/size limits.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m@@ [0m[1;36m-358[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m7[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m399[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m @@[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                 && [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == J;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39misStream || isObj[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                         [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-                            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m we're done reading this object![0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                             return true;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Patch [0m[33mResult[0m[39m===[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reports a libFuzzer timeout error, indicating that the fuzzing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocess exceeded its execution time limit. A patch was attempted to address this [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout by introducing various parsing limits and depth controls in the PDF parser [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode, specifically in the `BaseParser.java` and `COSParser.java` files. However, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter applying the patch, the timeout error persists, suggesting that the [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimplemented safeguards are either insufficient, not properly enforced, or the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout occurs in code paths not covered by the modifications.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a libFuzzer timeout error. This type of error occurs when the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer's execution of the target code exceeds a predefined time threshold. Timeout [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merrors in fuzzing typically indicate one or more of the following scenarios:[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The code enters an infinite or very long-running loop[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Recursive operations without proper termination conditions[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Processing of pathologically crafted input that leads to exponential time [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomplexity[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inefficient algorithms processing malformed or adversarial input data[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIn the context of a PDF parser [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPDFBox[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, timeout issues are commonly associated [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith parsing malformed or maliciously crafted PDF files that exploit parser [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvulnerabilities to consume excessive computational resources.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch introduces several defensive mechanisms to prevent excessive resource [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconsumption during PDF parsing:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `COSParser.java`:**[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Adds a constant `MAX_STREAM_SIZE` set to 500MB [0m[1;39m([0m[39m500L * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, intended to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimit the maximum size of streams that can be processed.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `BaseParser.java`:**[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Introduces parsing state tracking variables:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `parsingDepth`: tracks the current nesting depth during parsing[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `totalParsingOperations`: counts total parsing operations performed[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Defines several protective constants:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `MAX_PARSING_DEPTH`: set to [0m[1;36m25[0m[39m, limits recursion depth[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `MAX_COLLECTION_ELEMENTS`: set to [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m, limits elements in collections[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `MAX_STRING_LENGTH`: set to 10MB[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `MAX_ERROR_RECOVERY_BYTES`: set to 1MB, limits error recovery attempts[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `MAX_TOTAL_OPERATIONS`: set to [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m, limits total parsing operations[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Implements three control methods:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `[0m[1;35mincreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: increments depth counter and throws IOException if [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaximum is exceeded[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `[0m[1;35mdecreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: decrements depth counter with error logging for [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnegative values[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `[0m[1;35mcheckTotalOperations[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: increments operation counter and throws IOException [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif maximum is exceeded[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Modifications to `[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method:**[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Adds `[0m[1;35mcheckTotalOperations[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call at the beginning[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Wraps the entire parsing logic in a try-finally block with [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mincreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mdecreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to track recursion depth[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Introduces `elementCount` variable to track dictionary elements[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Enforces `MAX_COLLECTION_ELEMENTS` limit by throwing IOException when exceeded[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Returns appropriate error context including offset positions in error messages[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Modifications to `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method:**[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Introduces `bytesRead` counter to track bytes read during error recovery[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Enforces `MAX_ERROR_RECOVERY_BYTES` limit by throwing IOException when exceeded[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Removes a comment about stopping conditions while keeping the logic intact[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Result[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the libFuzzer timeout error persists unchanged. This [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicates that:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The timeout may be occurring in code paths not covered by the modifications[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. The limits set in the patch may be too generous to prevent the timeout within [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe fuzzer's time constraints[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. The timeout might be caused by operations other than dictionary parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39msuch as[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream processing, object resolution, or other parsing operations[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. The `MAX_STREAM_SIZE` constant was defined but may not be actively enforced in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream processing code[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas Requiring Further Investigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo gain a holistic understanding of the timeout issue, the following areas of the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcodebase should be investigated:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Stream Processing Code**: The `MAX_STREAM_SIZE` constant was added but its [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menforcement mechanism is not visible in the patch. Investigate where and how [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstreams are processed and whether size limits are properly enforced.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Other Parsing Methods**: The patch only modifies `[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. Other parsing methods such as:[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Array parsing methods[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Object parsing methods[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Cross-reference table parsing[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stream content parsing[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   These may also need similar protective measures.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Object Resolution and Indirect References**: PDF parsers often follow indirect[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobject references, which can create cycles or deep chains. Investigate how the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparser handles:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Indirect object resolution[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Circular references[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Deep object reference chains[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **The `totalParsingOperations` Counter**: While defined and checked in [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, investigate whether this counter needs to be checked in [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother parsing methods or loops throughout the codebase.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Loop Constructs**: Identify all while-loops and for-loops in the parsing code [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto determine if they have proper termination conditions and guards against [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed input.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Recursive Calls**: Map all recursive calling patterns in the parser to ensure [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe depth tracking covers all recursion paths, not just dictionary parsing.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **Input Validation**: Review where input data sizes, offsets, and lengths are [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidated before being used in loops or memory allocation operations.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. **Fuzzer Test Case**: If available, analyzing the specific input that causes the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout would help identify which code path is consuming excessive time.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/BaseParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:1443[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1461[0m          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1443[0m[39m:    protected final StringBuilder [0m[1;35mreadStringNumber[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1444[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1445[0m[39m:        int lastByte;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1446[0m[39m:        StringBuilder buffer = new [0m[1;35mStringBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1447[0m[39m:        while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35misDigit[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlastByte = [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1453[0m[39m:                        [0m[32m"' is getting too long, stop reading at offset "[0m[39m + [0m    [2m                [0m
