[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1454[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1455[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1456[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m lastByte != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m [0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1457[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1458[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35msource.rewind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1459[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1460[0m[39m:        return buffer;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1461[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis Summary[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter thoroughly analyzing the code snippets and evaluation report, I've identified[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhy the previous patch failed and what comprehensive fix is needed:[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Causes of Timeout[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Incomplete Recursion Protection**: The patch only added depth tracking to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`parseCOSDictionary`, but recursion flows through multiple paths:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `parseDirObject` → `parseCOSDictionary` → `parseCOSDictionaryValue` → [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`parseDirObject` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecursive loop[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `parseDirObject` → `parseCOSArray` → `parseDirObject` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecursive loop without [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mANY depth tracking[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mixed recursion: Dictionary → Array → Dictionary → Array [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbypasses [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdictionary-only depth limit[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Unbounded String/Name Parsing**: Multiple methods have unbounded loops without[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize limits:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `parseCOSString`: reads until balanced parentheses, no size limit[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `parseCOSHexString`: reads until [0m[32m'>'[0m[39m, no size limit[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `parseCOSName`: reads until end-of-name marker, no size limit[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `MAX_STRING_LENGTH` constant was defined but never enforced[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Unbounded Stream Processing**: `readUntilEndStream` can read indefinitely [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msearching for ENDSTREAM/ENDOBJ markers. The `MAX_STREAM_SIZE` constant was added [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut never used.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Unbounded Utility Loops**: `skipSpaces` is called very frequently and has [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munbounded loops for whitespace/comments with no limits.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Array Element Count**: `parseCOSArray` has no element count limit [0m[1;39m([0m[39munlike the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatched dictionary which added `MAX_COLLECTION_ELEMENTS`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why Previous Patch Failed[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch attempted to protect only `parseCOSDictionary`, but:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Timeout can occur through deeply nested arrays alone[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Timeout can occur through mixed array/dictionary nesting[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Timeout can occur in string/name parsing with malformed input[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Timeout can occur in stream processing[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The depth tracking was local to dictionary parsing, not global across all [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Unified Depth Tracking in `parseDirObject`[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `BaseParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:948[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1016[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparseDirObject method[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Move depth tracking from `parseCOSDictionary` to `parseDirObject` since it's the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcentral dispatcher for all recursive parsing[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add `[0m[1;35mincreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call at the beginning of `parseDirObject`[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Use try-finally block to ensure `[0m[1;35mdecreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is always called[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This covers ALL recursive paths: dictionaries, arrays, and mixed structures[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: `parseDirObject` is the single entry point for all recursive parsing[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations. By protecting it, we protect against deep recursion regardless of [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhether it's through dictionaries, arrays, or mixed structures.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Add Element Count Limit to `parseCOSArray`[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `BaseParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:755[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m822[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparseCOSArray method[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add an element counter variable [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlike the patch did for dictionary[0m[1;39m)[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check against `MAX_COLLECTION_ELEMENTS` on each iteration[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException when limit exceeded[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Keep the existing error recovery logic intact[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: Arrays can be as large as dictionaries and need the same protection.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch only protected dictionaries, leaving arrays vulnerable.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Enforce String Size Limits in `parseCOSString`[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `BaseParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:528[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m679[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparseCOSString method[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Track bytes written to `ByteArrayOutputStream`[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check against `MAX_STRING_LENGTH` after each write operation[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException when limit exceeded[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Provide offset information in error message[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: The `MAX_STRING_LENGTH` constant was defined but never enforced. PDF[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstrings should not be arbitrarily large.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Enforce String Size Limits in `parseCOSHexString`[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `BaseParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:693[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m746[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparseCOSHexString method[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Track `StringBuilder` length during accumulation[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check against `MAX_STRING_LENGTH` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdivided by [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m for hex since [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m hex chars = [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbyte[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException when limit exceeded[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: Hex strings have the same issue as literal strings and need size [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimits.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Enforce Name Size Limits in `parseCOSName`[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `BaseParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:861[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m918[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparseCOSName method[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Track `ByteArrayOutputStream` size during accumulation[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check against a reasonable name length limit [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m127[0m[39m bytes, as PDF names are [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtypically short identifiers[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Define new constant `MAX_NAME_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m127[0m[39m`[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException when limit exceeded[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: PDF names are typically short identifiers. A maliciously long name [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcould cause timeout.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Enforce Stream Size Limits in `readUntilEndStream`[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `COSParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:793[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m885[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreadUntilEndStream method[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add a `totalBytesRead` counter that accumulates across all buffer reads[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check against `MAX_STREAM_SIZE` after each buffer read[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException when limit exceeded[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The `[0m[1;35mout.calculateLength[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` result should also be validated against the limit[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: The `MAX_STREAM_SIZE` constant exists but is never enforced. Streams[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshould have size limits to prevent reading indefinitely.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m. Add Iteration Limits to `skipSpaces`[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `BaseParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:1319[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1343[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mskipSpaces method[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add an iteration counter for the main loop[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Define new constant `MAX_WHITESPACE_SEQUENCE = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m` for reasonable [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhitespace/comment sequences[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException when limit exceeded[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: `skipSpaces` is called very frequently. If input consists primarily [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof whitespace or comments, the cumulative time spent here could cause timeout.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m. Reapply Dictionary Protection with Depth Tracking Removed[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `BaseParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:281[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m328[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparseCOSDictionary method[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes from previous patch**:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Keep the `[0m[1;35mcheckTotalOperations[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call at the beginning[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Keep the element count tracking and `MAX_COLLECTION_ELEMENTS` limit[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Keep the try-finally structure but **remove the depth tracking calls** [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`increaseParsingDepth`[0m[35m/[0m[39m`decreaseParsingDepth`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m since depth tracking is now in [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`parseDirObject`[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Keep all error recovery improvements[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: The dictionary-specific protections are good, but depth tracking [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshould be unified in `parseDirObject`, not duplicated per method.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m9[0m[39m. Add Operation Counter and Total Operations Check[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: Throughout BaseParser [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmultiple methods[0m[1;39m)[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The `totalParsingOperations` counter and `[0m[1;35mcheckTotalOperations[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method from the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevious patch should be kept[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add `[0m[1;35mcheckTotalOperations[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls at the beginning of:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `parseCOSArray` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbefore loop starts[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `parseCOSString` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbefore loop starts[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `parseCOSHexString` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbefore loop starts[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `parseCOSName` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbefore loop starts[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `readUntilEndStream` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbefore loop starts[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: This provides a safety net for cumulative overhead across all [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing operations, catching cases where many small operations add up to timeout.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m. Define All Constants in BaseParser[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `BaseParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:166[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m176[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter document field[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Constants to add/keep**:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected int parsingDepth = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected long totalParsingOperations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_PARSING_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m25[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_COLLECTION_ELEMENTS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_STRING_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_NAME_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m127[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m PDF spec typical limit[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_ERROR_RECOVERY_BYTES = [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m MB[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_WHITESPACE_SEQUENCE = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final long MAX_TOTAL_OPERATIONS = [0m[1;36m1000000[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In COSParser.java**:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final long MAX_STREAM_SIZE = 500L * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m500[0m[39m MB[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m11[0m[39m. Add Helper Methods to BaseParser[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `BaseParser.java` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter getObjectFromPool method, around line [0m[1;36m270[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Methods to add/keep**:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected void [0m[1;35mincreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected void [0m[1;35mdecreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected void [0m[1;35mcheckTotalOperations[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThese methods should have the same implementation as in the previous patch, with [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproper error messages including offset information.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Implementation Order and Critical Considerations[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Implementation Steps:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **First**: Add all constants and helper methods to `BaseParser` and `COSParser`[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Second**: Implement unified depth tracking in `parseDirObject` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmost critical [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfix[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Third**: Add size limits to string/name parsing methods[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Fourth**: Add element count limit to `parseCOSArray`[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Fifth**: Enforce stream size limit in `readUntilEndStream`[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Sixth**: Add iteration limit to `skipSpaces`[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **Seventh**: Reapply dictionary protections [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwithout duplicate depth tracking[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. **Eighth**: Add operation counter checks to all major parsing methods[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Preserving Existing Logic:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Never remove error recovery code**: All existing LOG.warn and error handling [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpaths must be preserved[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Never change parser tolerance**: Keep all `isLenient` checks and lenient [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing behavior[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Never modify validation thresholds**: Keep existing constants like [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`OBJECT_NUMBER_THRESHOLD`, `GENERATION_NUMBER_THRESHOLD`[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Never change character classification**: Keep all utility methods like [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`isDigit`, `isHexDigit`, `isEOL` unchanged[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Never modify encryption/security handling**: Keep all `securityHandler` [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minteractions unchanged[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Error Messages:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAll IOException messages should include:[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- What limit was exceeded and its value[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Current position in stream [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Context information [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[32m"in dictionary"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"in array"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"in string"[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExample: `[0m[32m"Maximum parsing depth exceeded: "[0m[39m + MAX_PARSING_DEPTH + [0m[32m" at offset "[0m[39m + [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Fix Will Succeed:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Comprehensive Coverage**: Protects all timeout-prone code paths identified in [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39manalysis[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Unified Depth Tracking**: Single depth counter in `parseDirObject` covers all [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdictionaries, arrays, mixed[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Size Limits**: Enforces all defined constants [0m[1;39m([0m[39mMAX_STRING_LENGTH, [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_STREAM_SIZE, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Multiple Defense Layers**: Depth limit + size limits + operation counter [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprovide overlapping protection[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Follows Existing Patterns**: Uses same design patterns already present in [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcodebase [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreadStringNumber, PDFStreamEngine[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Conservative Limits**: All limits are set high enough for legitimate PDFs but [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlow enough to prevent timeout[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Legitimate deeply nested PDFs might be rejected**: [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: [0m[33mMAX_PARSING_DEPTH[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m25[0m[39m is quite generous, deeper nesting is rare[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If needed, make configurable via system property[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Large legitimate strings might be rejected**:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: [0m[33mMAX_STRING_LENGTH[0m[39m=[0m[35m10MB[0m[39m is very large, sufficient for legitimate [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muse[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If needed, make configurable via system property[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Performance overhead from frequent checks**:[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: Counter increments and integer comparisons are negligible overhead[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only adds a few nanoseconds per operation[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Different error messages**:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: New errors clearly indicate resource limits exceeded, helping [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39musers identify malformed PDFs[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reports a [0m[32m"libFuzzer: timeout"[0m[39m error, indicating that the fuzzing[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocess exceeded its time limit while testing the codebase. The patch attempt [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintroduced various parsing constraints and limits to the PDF parsing code in Apache[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDFBox, including maximum parsing depth, collection element limits, string length [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimits, and total operation counts. Despite these additions, the patch result shows[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat the timeout error persists, suggesting that the introduced constraints did not[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msuccessfully address the root cause of the timeout.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a timeout error encountered during libFuzzer testing. This [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicates that the fuzzer was unable to complete execution within the allocated [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtime limit. Timeout errors in fuzzing typically occur when the code under test [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menters an infinite or extremely long-running loop, performs excessive recursive [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations, or processes input in an inefficient manner that scales poorly with [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcertain input patterns.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt Analysis[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch introduces several defensive mechanisms across two files in the PDF [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing module:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `COSParser.java`:**[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Added a constant `MAX_STREAM_SIZE` set to 500MB [0m[1;39m([0m[39m500L * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This constant is defined but not actually used in any parsing logic within the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvisible patch[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `BaseParser.java`:**[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Added instance variables to track parsing state:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `parsingDepth`: tracks current recursion depth[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `totalParsingOperations`: tracks total number of parsing operations[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Added multiple constraint constants:[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `MAX_PARSING_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m25[0m[39m`: maximum allowed parsing depth[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `MAX_COLLECTION_ELEMENTS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`: maximum elements in collections[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `MAX_STRING_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m`: maximum string length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m10MB[0m[1;39m)[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `MAX_NAME_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m127[0m[39m`: maximum name length[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `MAX_ERROR_RECOVERY_BYTES = [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m`: maximum bytes to read during error [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecovery [0m[1;39m([0m[39m1MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas for Further Investigation[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBased on the patch attempt and its failure to resolve the timeout, the following [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mareas should be investigated:[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Unused Constants**: The `MAX_STREAM_SIZE`, `MAX_STRING_LENGTH`, [0m               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Array and String Parsing**: Methods that parse PDF arrays [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mparseCOSArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Stream Processing**: The `MAX_STREAM_SIZE` constant suggests concern about [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream processing, but no stream parsing logic modifications are visible. The [0m      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39munbounded operations.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Object Reference Resolution**: The `[0m[1;35mgetObjectFromPool[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method and object [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreference resolution logic should be examined for potential circular references or [0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Whitespace Handling**: Despite defining `MAX_WHITESPACE_SEQUENCE`, the [0m        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m873[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Prior to PDF v1.[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m, the # was not a special character.  Also,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m874[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m it has been observed that various PDF tools do not follow [0m   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m875[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m spec with respect to the # escape, even though they report[0m   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m877[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m interpret the # as an escape only when it is followed by two[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m880[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m177[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m178[0m[39m:    private static boolean [0m[1;35misHexDigit[0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar ch[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m179[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m180[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35misDigit[0m[1;39m([0m[39mch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ||[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m181[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m([0m[39mch >= [0m[32m'a'[0m[39m && ch <= [0m[32m'f'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ||[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m182[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m([0m[39mch >= [0m[32m'A'[0m[39m && ch <= [0m[32m'F'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m183[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m185[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m186[0m[39m:     * Returns the object key for the given combination of object and [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgeneration number. The object key from the cross[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m187[0m[39m:     * reference table/stream will be reused if available. Otherwise a newly [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcreated object will be returned.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m188[0m[39m:     * [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m189[0m[39m:     * @param num the given object number[0m                                       [2m                [0m
