[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:     * [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:     * @return the COS object key[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:    protected COSObjectKey [0m[1;35mgetObjectKey[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlong num, int gen[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdocument == null || [0m[1;35mdocument.getXrefTable[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.isEmpty[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:            return new [0m[1;35mCOSObjectKey[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnum, gen[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m use a cache to get the COSObjectKey as iterating over the [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mxref-table-map gets slow for big pdfs[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis of the Timeout Issue[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter analyzing the code snippets and the evaluation report, I've identified that [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe previous patch attempt only partially addressed the timeout issue. While it [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madded several constraint constants and tracking mechanisms, it failed to apply most[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof them to the actual parsing methods that have unbounded loops.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Core Problems Identified[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **`[0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method** - Has unbounded loops for whitespace and comments with[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mno iteration limits[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **String parsing methods** - `[0m[1;35mparseCOSHexString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mparseCOSString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparseCOSName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` lack length checks[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Array parsing** - `[0m[1;35mparseCOSArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` lacks element count limits[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Stream parsing** - `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` lacks size limits[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Recursion tracking** - Never implemented despite being defined in the failed [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Other utility methods** - `[0m[1;35mreadString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mparseCOSNumber[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mskipWhiteSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` lack bounds[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Fix Strategy[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix strategy will comprehensively address all identified timeout vectors by [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplying bounds checking to every unbounded loop in the parsing code. This approach[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfollows existing patterns in the codebase [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlike `[0m[1;35mreadStringNumber[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and will [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevent fuzzer timeouts while maintaining compatibility with legitimate PDFs.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Add and Initialize Tracking Variables in BaseParser[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/BaseParser.java`[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd instance variables after line [0m[1;36m168[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter `protected COSDocument document;`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Parsing depth tracking for recursion protection[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected int parsingDepth = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Total operations counter to prevent excessive parsing time[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected long totalParsingOperations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd constraint constants after line [0m[1;36m168[0m[39m:[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_PARSING_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m25[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_COLLECTION_ELEMENTS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_STRING_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m 10MB[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_NAME_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m127[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_ERROR_RECOVERY_BYTES = [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m 1MB[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_WHITESPACE_SEQUENCE = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final long MAX_TOTAL_OPERATIONS = [0m[1;36m1000000[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected static final int MAX_NUMBER_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Reasonable limit for PDF [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnumbers[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Add Helper Methods for Tracking in BaseParser[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: After the `[0m[1;35mgetObjectFromPool[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m280[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd these helper methods:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected void [0m[1;35mincreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++parsingDepth > MAX_PARSING_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Maximum parsing depth exceeded: "[0m[39m + [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_PARSING_DEPTH + [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[32m" at offset "[0m[39m + [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected void [0m[1;35mdecreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    parsingDepth--;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparsingDepth < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mLOG.error[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Parsing depth is negative: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m[39m, parsingDepth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        parsingDepth = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected void [0m[1;35mcheckTotalOperations[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++totalParsingOperations > MAX_TOTAL_OPERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Maximum total parsing operations exceeded: "[0m[39m + [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                MAX_TOTAL_OPERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m13[0m[39m. Fix `[0m[1;35mparseDirObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` Method[0m                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis is the central recursive method that needs depth tracking:[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add recursion depth tracking at the beginning:[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Call `[0m[1;35mincreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` after line [0m[1;36m950[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter skipSpaces[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Wrap the entire method body in try-finally[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Call `[0m[1;35mdecreaseParsingDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in the finally block[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This will track recursion through arrays, dictionaries, and nested structures[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m14[0m[39m. Add Stream Size Limit in COSParser[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/COSParser.java`[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mModify `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m793[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m885[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add a constant `MAX_STREAM_SIZE = 100L * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m100MB instead of 500MB for[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfaster timeout[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add a `totalBytesRead` counter before the outer while loop[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In each iteration, add the number of bytes read to the counter[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check if `totalBytesRead > MAX_STREAM_SIZE` and throw IOException if exceeded[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This prevents extremely large streams from causing timeouts[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe 100MB limit is more appropriate than the 500MB from the failed patch because:[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fuzzer timeouts occur quickly, so we need to fail fast[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Legitimate PDFs rarely have streams this large in normal use[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This still allows reasonably large documents while preventing fuzzer abuse[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m15[0m[39m. Apply Bounds to `[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionaryValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` Method[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: Around line [0m[1;36m404[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m406[0m[39m in BaseParser.java [0m[1;39m([0m[39mneed to retrieve this method[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis method is called by `[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionaryNameValuePair[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and likely calls [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparseDirObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No specific changes needed if it simply delegates to `[0m[1;35mparseDirObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The recursion depth tracking in `[0m[1;35mparseDirObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` will protect this path[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Implementation Order and Dependencies[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. First, add all constants and instance variables to BaseParser[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add the helper methods [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincreaseParsingDepth, decreaseParsingDepth, [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheckTotalOperations[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Fix the utility methods first [0m[1;39m([0m[39mskipSpaces, skipWhiteSpaces, readString[0m[1;39m)[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Fix the primitive parsing methods [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparseCOSName, parseCOSNumber, parseCOSString,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparseCOSHexString[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Fix the collection parsing methods [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparseCOSArray, parseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m)[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Add recursion tracking to parseDirObject[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Fix stream parsing in COSParser[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Key Design Principles[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Follow existing patterns**: Use the same pattern as `[0m[1;35mreadStringNumber[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` for [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength checks[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Use try-finally for recursion tracking**: Ensures depth counter is always [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdecremented[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Include position information in errors**: Helps with debugging and error [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreporting[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Conservative limits**: Set limits that are generous for legitimate PDFs but [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevent fuzzer abuse[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Fail fast**: Throw exceptions immediately when limits are exceeded rather than[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrying to recover[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **No modification to harness or test code**: All changes are in the production [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparser code only[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Justification[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis comprehensive fix strategy addresses all timeout vectors identified in the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Unbounded loops**: All loops that read characters/bytes now have iteration or [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize limits[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Recursive calls**: All recursive parsing paths now track depth and enforce a [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaximum[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Total operations**: A global operation counter prevents cumulative timeout from[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmany small operations[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Stream processing**: Large stream reading now has a size limit[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe approach preserves all existing logic:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Error recovery mechanisms remain intact[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- PDF specification compliance is maintained[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All validation and special case handling is preserved[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fixes only add bounds checking, not logic changes[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Legitimate large PDFs might fail**: The limits are set conservatively high [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m10MB strings, 100MB streams, [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m collection elements[0m[1;39m)[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Deeply nested structures might fail**: The [0m[1;36m25[0m[39m-level recursion depth limit [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatches the failed patch and should be sufficient for valid PDFs[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Error messages might change**: New IOExceptions will be thrown with [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdescriptive messages about limit violations[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThese are acceptable trade-offs because:[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer timeout is the critical issue that must be resolved[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Extremely large or deeply nested PDFs are rare in legitimate use[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The error messages will help identify the specific limit that was exceeded[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The limits can be adjusted if needed based on real-world testing[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
